<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-02-0160 </DOCNO><TEXT>The transfer of radiation in the wings of lines has been investigatedfor the case when the scattering is coherent in the atom's frame of reference.Exact analytical solutions have been found for an approximate equationwhich describes the diffusion of photons in a conservative medium. Theaccuracy of the approximation and the limits of its applicability havebeen determined by means of a comparison with numerical solutions ofthe exact equation.</TEXT></DOC>